        <item>
            <title>2.7.2</title>
            <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jul 2026 23:23:42 +0900</pubDate>
            <link>https://github.com/Saqoosha/Canopy</link>
            <sparkle:version>71</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>2.7.2</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>15.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <sparkle:hardwareRequirements>arm64</sparkle:hardwareRequirements>
            <description sparkle:format="markdown"><![CDATA[### Bug Fixes
- Fixed sessions appearing twice in the sidebar — once in the open list and again in Recents — when the CLI ignored the launcher-supplied resume UUID (no matching JSONL) and picked its own session ID. The same session could also be reopened as a fresh row from Recents.
- Fixed AI-generated session titles being lost when a fresh session first reported its real session ID — titles are now re-keyed from the placeholder ID to the real one.
]]></description>
